2C9DD90C.Line27.EFA01: I should get going now. Here's somethin' for your trouble.

31F0F7AA.Line34.EFA01: What for? ...oh, you mean Flinn? Don't be.

7CD404D9.VoiceDir27.EFA01: Thanking the player, saying goodbye. She has somewhere to be.

82272377.VoiceDir34.EFA01: Confused at first. She's not sure why the player is apologizing

92A95F8A.Line25.EFA01: Sure was. Shame he had to go that way. Appreciate your help, though.

97FC7E28.Line32.EFA01: These things tend to happen round here. You get used to it - ya have to. Backwater ain't for the faint of heart.

E832A9F5.VoiceDir32.EFA01: Again, not cold; just pragmatic. For the last sentence only, a bit knowingly/amused.
